title: FHA, Defaults and foreclosures of FHA-backed home loans in Atlanta HOC, Jan 2009
name: FHA, Defaults and foreclosures of FHA-backed home loans in Atlanta HOC, Jan 2009
description:
The point shape file shows the number of defaults and foreclosures by zipcode in the Atlanta HOC region of all home loans originated between Jan 31, 2007 to Jan 31, 2009 that are backed by FHA home insurance. 
HUD (Housing and Urban Devp) has four regional centers located in Atlanta, Denver, Philadelphia and Santa Ana. 
Look for defaults and foreclosure data for other regions elsewhere on Finder! using key word "FHA" or "HOC" 

https://entp.hud.gov/sfnw/public/

author.source: FHA/HUD's website: Early Warning Neighborhood Watch
